Packages 
Package Description
application
Package with the Main method
conccurent
Package to host all the classes wich deal with threads
conccurent.refresh
This Package handle the refresh of some GUI elements, table and the global bar
error
Package to handle error message
gui.controller
Package that host all the controller of the relative fxml files
gui.fxml
Package for host all the FXML files
gui.logic
Package for handle some GUI logic componenets action
gui.progress
Package for update the progress of the progressColumn and the Globa Bar
job.input
Intput branch of job is used by JobInStarter for set the element to process via stream.input package
job.output
Output branch of job is used by JobOutStarter for set the element to process via stream.output package
jobStarter
Package for process the list via JobListSelector and redirect the job to the right input JobInStarter or output JobOutStarter process
jobStarter.input
Input branch of jobStarter
jobStarter.output
Output branch of jobStarter
logic
The package Logic handle all the hard logic of the program, like the definition of the list elements via FileElement the Observable list manipulator FSlistFileElement, the header package for the header creatioin and reading, and the FSPasswordHash to handle the crypt/decrypt operations
logic.header
This package manage the Header Logic of the program, when a file is processed by the program is created an header File with all the info of the operation This header have the extension ".0.sp" and is a generic txt with 6 rows (starting from 0) with this fields:
stream
The Stream Package porpouse is to handle all the IO operation with StreamCore and divide them for reconstruct a file with stream.input package or split a file with stream.output package and the specialized class for the type of operations (split,crypt,compress) all the operation are called by job package
stream.input
Input branch of stream, host the InputCore abstract class used by InputSplit, InputDecrypt and InputDecompress For process a single FileElement
stream.output
Output branch of stream, host the OutputCore abstract class used by OutputSplit, OutputCrypt and OutputCompress For process a single FileElement
